summary: ...JERRY EXPECTED TO BE NEAR THE NORTHERN LEEWARD ISLANDS LATER TODAY... ...TROPICAL STORM WARNING ISSUED FOR BARBUDA... As of 11:00 AM AST Thu Oct 09 the center of Jerry was located near 15.9, -59.1 with movement WNW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 999 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
